main event: A civilian observed an unidentified object moving up and down in the sky for 2 hours in Newport, Kentucky.
interesting points: The object was described as being round with a bright light in the center.
The witnesses were looking skyward and may have been watching an astronomical body.
There is no indication of difficulty or directives to determine what was observed.
The Air Force requested the witness complete a report form for further evaluation.
No photographs were taken of the object.
sighted object: round object with a bright light in the center
